      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_033_000057",
    "sentence": "凡爾中外，宜體朕懷。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_033_000058",
    "sentence": "辛丑，授魏王繼岌諸道行營都統，餘如故。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_033_000059",
